B.m6=new A.fH("Rajesh Kumar","New Delhi","RK","Sandeep ji's Kundli reading was unlike anything I had experienced before. He described events from my past with startling accuracy \u2014 things no one could have known. His guidance on my career transition proved to be exactly right. I changed jobs during the muhurta he suggested and within six months I received a promotion. Highly recommend for anyone seeking genuine astrological counsel.","Kundli Analysis")
B.m3=new A.fH("Priya Sharma","Mumbai","PS","I was sceptical about Kundli Milan before my engagement, but my mother insisted. Sandeep ji not only matched our charts but also pointed out a specific challenge we would face in the third year of marriage \u2014 and he was absolutely right. More importantly, he gave us remedies and today we are stronger than ever. His insight is a gift.","Kundli Milan")
B.m4=new A.fH("Vikram Mehta","Pune","VM","Our office had been struggling with losses for two years despite a good team and product. After Sandeep ji's Vastu consultation, we made a few inexpensive changes \u2014 mainly the placement of the cash counter and the direction of my desk. Within three months, revenue doubled. It sounds impossible but the results are undeniable.","Vastu Shastra")
B.m1=new A.fH("Sunita Agarwal","Jaipur","SA","I consulted Sandeep ji through a Prashna Kundli about a property dispute that had dragged on for four years. Within 20 minutes he told me the case would resolve in my favour within four months, and it did \u2014 exactly 3 months and 22 days later. His command over Vedic horary astrology is exceptional.","Prashna Kundli")
B.m5=new A.fH("Amit Patel","Ahmedabad","AP","The gemstone consultation changed my life. I was wearing a diamond (Shukra) which Sandeep ji immediately identified as harmful for my chart. He prescribed a yellow sapphire instead. Within weeks I felt a notable shift in clarity and confidence. Three months in, I closed a deal I had been chasing for over a year.","Gemstone Consultation")
B.m2=new A.fH("Neha Gupta","Bengaluru","NG","I had severe Mangal dosha and had faced two broken engagements. Sandeep ji's remedies \u2014 a specific mantra practice and a brief puja \u2014 gave me peace I had not felt in years. I met my husband eight months later, and we have been happily married for three years now. I am forever grateful for his compassionate guidance.","Remedial Astrology")
